/midtown-church-page-header-background.jpg);\">\r\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"container\">\r\n                <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\r\n                    <h1 title=\"Purpose and Vision of Midtown Church - Central Austin and Campus Ministry\">Purpose &amp; Vision</h1>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section>\r\n	<div class=\"container\">\r\n		<div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-12 text-center\">\r\n				<h2 class=\"h-lines hl-2\">Midtown Church</h2>\r\n				<p class=\"lead\">A family loved and served by God, compelled to love and serve Austin with God.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"bg-dark-teal\">\r\n	<div class=\"container\">\r\n		<div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-12 text-center\">\r\n				<h2 class=\"h-lines hl-3\">Vision</h2>\r\n				<p class=\"lead\">Our central purpose is to glorify God in all things. Our vision is to partner with God to see the day when every man, woman and child hears the gospel from a person who loves them &mdash; beginning in Austin and spreading to the ends of the earth.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"bg-light-gray\">\r\n	<div class=\"container\">\r\n		<div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n				<img src=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/love-church-central-austin.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive img-thumbnail\">\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-9\">\r\n				<h3>Love</h3>\r\n				<p><strong><em>(Matthew 22:36-40)</em></strong><br>\r\nWe love God because God loved us first. He loved us when we didn’t love Him. He loves us when we fail to love Him. We love Him because he knows everything about us and still loves us. God loves us, therefore we love God.</p>\r\n				<p>We love people because people matter to God. God loves everyone; every man, woman & child. Which means God loves imperfect people like us and so we love imperfect people too. God loves people, therefore we love people.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-3 col-sm-push-9\">\r\n				<img src=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/serving-one-another-in-austin.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive img-thumbnail\">\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-9 col-sm-pull-3\">\r\n				<h3>Serve</h3>\r\n				<p><strong><em>(Mark 10:45)</em></strong><br>\r\nJesus came to serve. He gave his life serving. As his followers we chose to use our lives to serve. We chose to serve people who are not like us and who do not like us. We serve people who ask and people who don’t have a voice to ask. We serve the least, the hurting the lonely and the marginalized. We serve because people matter to God. We serve to give people a picture of our God who serves. Jesus came to serve, therefore we are here to serve.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n				<img src=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/central-austin-church.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive img-thumbnail\">\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-9\">\r\n				<h3>Austin</h3>\r\n				<p><strong><em>(Jeremiah 29:7)</em></strong><br>\r\n				God has given us a passion for our city; this is where we are called to love & serve.</p>\r\n				<p>We love Austin. We love its culture, its people and its places. As Central Austinites we want to do our part in helping Austin become an even more weird, fun, creative, green and loving city. We hope for a day that every person in Austin has an opportunity to hear about God’s love for them from a friend who loves them.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</section>','Purpose & Vision','','publish','closed','open','','purpose-vision','','','2015-08-07 18:47:46','2015-08-07 18:47:46','',0,'http://www.midtownaustin.org/?page_id=956',0,'page','',0),(958,1,'2015-08-03 15:31:05','201