ollege','','inherit','closed','open','','981-revision-v1','','','2015-08-04 00:36:04','2015-08-04 00:36:04','',981,'http://www.midtownaustin.org/2015/08/04/981-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(986,1,'2015-08-04 00:36:20','2015-08-04 00:36:20','<!-- Page Heading -->\r\n<!-- Parallax Section -->\r\n<section class=\"parallax parallax-giving\" style=\"background-image: url(http://previews.123rf.com/images/foodandmore/foodandmore1404/foodandmore140400150/27619776-Old-weathered-rustic-wooden-background-texture-with-vintage-brown-wood-boards-with-an-uneven-row-of--Stock-Photo.jpg);\">\r\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"container\">\r\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n                    <h1>Giving &mdash; An Act of Worship</h1>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n<!-- /.page heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- Page Content -->\r\n\r\n<section>\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 text-center\">\r\n                <p class=\"lead\">Jesus is the most generous person who ever lived. He gave his life so that we might live. As Christians, we give our time, talent, and money joyfully in response to Jesus’ generosity and to help more people meet Jesus.</p>\r\n\r\n                <p>As a community, we take joy in the ways our faith is made stronger through giving and receiving together. There is a satisfaction that comes from following Jesus’ example of generosity toward those most in need, and it is a privilege to use our resources and time to continue telling God’s story and help bring measurable change in the world.</p>\r\n\r\n                <p>Below are some ways for you to give to the ministry of Midtown Church.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"bg-light-gray\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"h-lines hl-2\">Ways to Give</h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-6 text-center\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"h-gray\">Online</h2>\r\n                <p>You can give via credit card or bank withdrawal either one time or recurring. Click the button below to begin.</p>\r\n                <p><a href=\"https://midtownchurch.cloverdonations.com/give/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"btn btn-warning btn-lg\">Click Here to Give Online</a></p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-6 text-center\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"h-gray\">Cash &amp; Checks</h2>\r\n                <p>Please make checks payable to Midtown Church and drop them in the offering plate on Sunday or mail to:</p>\r\n                <address>\r\n                    Midtown Church<br>\r\n                    4809 Sinclair Ave<br>\r\n                    Austin, TX 78756\r\n                </address>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section>\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"h-gray h-lines hl-1\">Volunteering</h2>\r\n                <p>If you’ve been served by Midtown Church, whether it be through greeters on Sundays, teachers in you child’s classroom, enjoying a cup of coffee before service, musicians on stage leading us in worship, or any number of other ways—chances are you’ve been served by a faithful volunteer giving up time and talent to serve Jesus by serving you. At Midtown, we intentionally keep our budget and staff small and rely on a community of volunteers who love Jesus and love to serve his church.</p>\r\n                <p>If you consider Midtown your church, we ask you to serve as a volunteer. By doing so, you’re an essential part of helping others meet Jesus. And if you’re a member, you’ve committed to serve generously as part of your membership covenant.</p>\r\n                <p>There are a number of opportunities to serve at Midtown. To find out how you can serve, contact Adam Brunson at adam@midtownaustin.org</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>','Give','','inherit','closed','open','','935-revision-v1','','','2015-08-04 00:36:20','2015-08-04 00:36:20','',935,'http://www.midtownaustin.org/2015/08/04/935-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(987,1,'2015-08-04 00:36:56','2015-08-04 00:36:56','<!-- Page Heading -->\r\n<!-- Parallax Section -->\r\n<section class=\"parallax parallax-mc\" style=\"background-image: url(https://scontent-dfw1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xaf1/t31.0-8/s2048x2048/10256695_519143751529359_361980284696071893_o.jpg);\">\r\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"container\">\r\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n                    <h1 title=\"Austin Church Small Groups\">Midtown Communities</h1>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n<!-- /.page heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- Page Content -->\r\n\r\n<section>\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n                <p >Midtown Church is a network of communities — small groups of 15-30 who get together at least weekly to connect like an extended family and grow in our love for God and people. Midtown Communities (MCs) are the primary way for people who are exploring Christianity to get connected to people who will love them and join with them in their journey.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n                <p>Whether you consider yourself part of the Midtown family — or if you’re just checking out what it looks like to live as Jesus lived — it is our desire that everyone would be an active member in one of these communities that bring life, healing and growth.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"bg-light-gray\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"h-lines hl-2\">Find a Group</h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n                <h4>Central Austin</h4>\r\n                <img src=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/central-austin-church-small-groups.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive img-thumbnail\">\r\n                <strong>Day / Time</strong>: Tuesdays @ 6:30pm<br>\r\n                <strong>Location</strong>: 7121 Hart lane #2124,\r\n                Austin, TX 78731<br>\r\n                <strong>Contact</strong>: alex.jentsch@utexas.edu\r\n                <p class=\"mc-desc\">The covenant of marriage is one of the biggest decisions anyone will make throughout their life. If you have recently tied the knot or are engaged to be married, then this is the perfect group for you. Come discuss scripture and find fellowship with others in the same life stage.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n                <h4>College Small Groups</h4>\r\n                <img src=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/college-campus-ministry-ut.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive img-thumbnail\">\r\n                <strong>Day / Time</strong>: Wednesdays @ 8:00pm<br>\r\n                <strong>Location</strong>: Varies (Check here for location)<br>\r\n                <strong>Contact</strong>: austinhill@utexas.edu\r\n                <p class=\"mc-desc\">These groups are specifically for college students looking for in depth community, accountability, an scripture. These groups meet on campus at the Texas Union together on Wednesday nights and then break up into small groups who will grow together in their knowledge of God as they study the Word.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n                <h4>Cross Cultural</h4>\r\n                <img src=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/cross-cultural-church-small-groups.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive img-thumbnail\">\r\n                <strong>Day / Time</strong>: Thursdays (Bi-Weekly) @ 7:00pm<br>\r\n                <strong>Location</strong>: 11117 Sandstone Trl Austin, TX 78750<br>\r\n                <strong>Contact</strong>: clintcagle@att.ne\r\n                <p class=\"mc-desc\">Small group in the North Austin area committed to reaching its neighbors. If you are passionate about reading scripture and want to work with others to pray for your neighbors and neighborhood, please join this group each Thursday night at 7PM.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section>\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n                <h4>Young Married</h4>\r\n                <img src=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/young-married-small-group.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive img-thumbnail\">\r\n                <strong>Day / Time</strong>: Tuesdays @ 6:30pm<br>\r\n                <strong>Location</strong>: 7121 Hart lane #2124,\r\n                Austin, TX 78731<br>\r\n                <strong>Contact</strong>: alex.jentsch@utexas.edu\r\n                <p class=\"mc-desc\">The covenant of marriage is one of the biggest decisions anyone will make throughout their life. If you have recently tied the knot or are engaged to be married, then this is the perfect group for you. Come discuss scripture and find fellowship with others in the same life stage.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n                <h4>College Small Groups</h4>\r\n                <img src=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/college-campus-ministry-ut.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive img-thumbnail\">\r\n                <strong>Day / Time</strong>: Wednesdays @ 8:00pm<br>\r\n                <strong>Location</strong>: Varies (Check here for location)<br>\r\n                <strong>Contact</strong>: austinhill@utexas.edu\r\n                <p class=\"mc-desc\">These groups are specifically for college students looking for in depth community, accountability, an scripture. These groups meet on campus at the Texas Union together on Wednesday nights and then break up into small groups who will grow together in their knowledge of God as they study the Word.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n                <h4>Cross Cultural</h4>\r\n                <img src=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/college-campus-ministry-ut.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive img-thumbnail\">\r\n                <strong>Day / Time</strong>: Thursdays (Bi-Weekly) @ 7:00pm<br>\r\n                <strong>Location</strong>: 11117 Sandstone Trl Austin, TX 78750<br>\r\n                <strong>Contact</strong>: clintcagle@att.ne\r\n                <p class=\"mc-desc\">Small group in the North Austin area committed to reaching its neighbors. If you are passionate about reading scripture and want to work with others to pray for your neighbors and neighborhood, please join this group each Thursday night at 7PM.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>','Midtown Communities','','inherit','closed','open','','939-revision-v1','','','2015-08-04 00:36:56','2015-08-04 00:36:56','',939,'http://www.midtownaustin.org/2015/08/04/939-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(988,1,'2015-08-04 00:37:31','2015-08-04 00:37:31','<section class=\"parallax parallax-giving\" style=\"background-image: url(https://scontent-dfw1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xaf1/t31.0-8/s2048x2048/10256695_519143751529359_361980284696071893_o.jpg);\">\r\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"container\">\r\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n                    <h1 title=\"About Midtown Church - Central Austin and Campus\">Who We Are</h1>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n              <div class=\"col-md-12 main-col\">\r\n                  <h1 class=\"font-bold\">Who We Is</h1>\r\n                  <p class=\"lead\">\r\n                  Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consetetur sadipscing elitr, sed diam nonumy eirmod tempor invidunt ut labore et dolore magna aliquyam erat, sed diam voluptua.\r\n                  </p>\r\n                  <div class=\"row\">\r\n                    <div class=\"col-md-6 bg-dark-teal\">\r\n                    <h4>Vision</h4>\r\n                    To see the day when every man, woman and child in Austin hears the gospel from a person who loves them. \r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"col-md-6 bg-dark-teal\">\r\n                    <h4>Identity</h4>\r\n                    Midtown Church is a family loved and served by God and committed to loving and serving Austin with God.\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n','Purpose & Vision','','inherit','closed','open','','956-revision-v1','','','2015-08-04 00:37:31','2015-08-04 00:37:31','',956,'http://www.midtownaustin.org/2015/08/04/956-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(989,1,'2015-08-04 00:38:20','2015-08-04 00:38:20','<script src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps/api/js?sensor=false\"></script>\r\n    <script>	\r\n \r\n      function init_map() {\r\n		var var_location = new google.maps.LatLng(30.3040961,-97.7355612);\r\n \r\n        var var_mapoptions = {\r\n          center: var_location,\r\n          zoom: 15\r\n        };\r\n \r\n		var var_marker = new google.maps.Marker({\r\n			position: var_location,\r\n			map: var_map,\r\n			title:\"Baker School Austin\"});\r\n		  \r\n		  var contentString = \r\n			\'<div id=\"infowindow_content\">\'+\r\n            \'<p><strong>Midtown Church</strong><br>\'+\r\n			\'Baker School<br>\'+\r\n            \'3908 Avenue B<br>\' +\r\n            \'Austin, TX 78751</p>\'+\r\n            \'<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/dir//Baker+School,+Austin,+TX+78751,+United+States/@30.3040961,-97.7355612,17z/data=!4m12!1m3!3m2!1s0x8644ca794f875311:0x703c57dd61b16770!2sBaker+School!4m7!1m0!1m5!1m1!1s0x8644ca794f875311:0x703c57dd61b16770!2m2!1d-97.7355612!2d30.3040961\" target=\"_blank\">Get Directions</a>\'+\r\n            \'</div>\';\r\n \r\n        var var_infowindow = new google.maps.InfoWindow({\r\n            content: contentString\r\n          });\r\n \r\n		var var_marker = new google.maps.Marker({\r\n			position: var_location,\r\n			map: var_map,\r\n			title:\"Click on marker to see info and get directions\",\r\n                  maxWidth: 500\r\n				  });\r\n \r\n		google.maps.event.addListener(var_marker, \'click\', function() {\r\n		var_infowindow.open(var_map,var_marker);\r\n		  });\r\n \r\n        var var_map = new google.maps.Map(document.getElementById(\"map-container\"),\r\n            var_mapoptions);\r\n \r\n		var_marker.setMap(var_map);	\r\n \r\n      }\r\n \r\n      google.maps.event.addDomListener(window, \'load\', init_map);\r\n \r\n    </script>\r\n\r\n<!-- Page Heading -->\r\n<!-- Parallax Section -->\r\n<section class=\"parallax parallax-sunday\" style=\"background-image: url(http://antiochcc.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Awaken_Day1_Worship_Antioch-Community-Church.jpg);\">\r\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"container\">\r\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n                    <h1 title=\"Central Austin and College Church Service\">Sunday Morning Gatherings</h1>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n<!-- /.page heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- Page Content -->\r\n\r\n<section>\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 text-center\">\r\n                <p class=\"lead\">Sunday Gatherings are a unique opportunity to gather around God to hear from his Word, consider his work, sing his praise, and enjoy his presence. They are also a place where those who are seeking, skeptical, or curious can come and explore the Christian faith with us.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"bg-light-gray\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"h-lines hl-2\">Where &amp; When</h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-5\">\r\n                <h4>The Baker School</h4>\r\n                <address>\r\n                    3908 Avenue B <br>\r\n                    Austin, TX 78751\r\n                </address>\r\n                <p>Doors open at 10:30am for snacks, delicious Anderson\'s Coffee, and/or\r\n                time to get your kiddos checked in for their class. Worship begins at\r\n                10:45am.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div id=\"map-container\" class=\"col-sm-7\"></div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section>\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-6 text-center\">\r\n                <h3>What to Expect</h3>\r\n                <p>When you get there, grab some coffee and meet someone or just head right into the auditorium. Knowing that Jesus has truly paid it all for us helps our worship environment have a relaxed and casual feel. We will sing some songs, hear a sermon about Jesus from the Bible, take communion, and say a few prayers. That’s about it! We welcome all people to join with us in our Sunday celebration of Jesus.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-6 text-center\">\r\n                <h3>What About Kids?</h3>\r\n                <p>While you are in the worship service we have fun and engaging classes for kids (nursery through elementary school) that will help them worship God according to their age level. We will always let you know what is being taught and classes are always optional.</p>\r\n                <p>We invite all middle school and high school students to worship with the adults.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>','Sunday Mornings','','inherit','closed','open','','923-revision-v1','','','2015-08-04 00:38:20','2015-08-04 00:38:20','',923,'http://www.midtownaustin.org/2015/08/04/923-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(990,1,'2015-08-04 01:34:43','2015-08-04 01:34:43','<section class=\"parallax parallax-sunday\" style=\"background-image: url(http://i.istockimg.com/image-zoom/17906621/3/380/253/zoom-17906621-3.jpg);\">\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"container\">\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\n                    <h1>Midtown Church College Ministry</h1>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\n				<h2 class=\"h-lines hl-2\">Midtown on Campus</h2>\n                <p class=\"lead\">Midotwn on Campus is committed to giving every student at the University of Texas the opportunity to experience the life-changing reality of Jesus Christ. Follow us on Twitter @HCBConCAMPUS for the most up to date information on events and meeting locations.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"bg-light-gray\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\n                <h2 class=\"h-gray h-lines hl-1\">Community Life</h2>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-sm-7\">\n				<h3>College Small Groups</h3>\n                <p>At Midtown Church, we long to grow in our relationship with God in the context of community. We believe this best happens as we are Godward, Inward, and Outward.</p>\n				<ul class=\"list-group\">\n					<li class=\"list-group-item\">\n						<strong>Godward</strong> &mdash; We strive to glorify God and enjoy Him in everything we do.\n					</li>\n					<li class=\"list-group-item\">\n						<strong>Inward</strong> &mdash; We believe it is vital that we invest deeply in each other and encourage each other to fully trust in Jesus.\n					</li>\n					<li class=\"list-group-item\">\n						<strong>Outward</strong> &mdash; We are committed to actively, intentionally, and consistently engaging people with the life-changing reality of Jesus Christ.\n					</li>\n				</ul>\n				<p>For Midtown on Campus, the majority of our small groups are on Wednesday nights in the Texas Union. We meet at 8pm for 30 - 45 minutes as one large group for worship, games, and a short talk before breaking up into small groups. This semester we are reading through Acts, Nehemiah, and Proverbs. If you are interested in joining a small group, come any Wednesday or email Brad at brad@midtownaustin.org.</p>\n            </div>\n			<div class=\"col-sm-5\">\n				<h3>Discipleship</h3>\n				<p>We believe that Jesus clearly gave the mandate in Matthew 28:18-20 to \"make disciples of all nations.\" At Mditown, one place we are committed to pursuing this commission is on the University of Texas Campus. We seek to provide all of our students the opportunity to both be discipled and engage in disciple-making which includes a specific focus in evangelism training. We believe that a multiplying movement of disciples is the most effective way to reach the ends of the earth with gospel, and we seek to labor with the strength of Christ to that end.</p>\n				<p>If you would like to learn more about our ministry philosophy on the campus of Texas, or if you would like to get involved in discipleship relationships and evangelism training then please contact Brad Laws at brad@midtownaustin.org</p>\n			</div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n			<div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\n				<h2 class=\"h-gray h-lines hl-1\">Upcoming Events</h2>\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n				[rpfc_recent_posts_from_category category=\"4\" posts=\"6\" excerpt=\"true\" container=\"col-sm-4\"]\n			</div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n','College','','inherit','closed','open','','981-autosave-v1','','','2015-08-04 01:34:43','2015-08-04 01:34:43','',981,'http://www.midtownaustin.org/2015/08/04/981-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(991,1,'2015-08-04 00:43:16','2015-08-04 00:43:16','<section class=\"parallax parallax-sunday\" style=\"background-image: url(http://i.istockimg.com/image-zoom/17906621/3/380/253/zoom-17906621-3.jpg);\">\r\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"container\">\r\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n                    <h1>Midtown Church College Ministry</h1>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section>\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 text-center\">\r\n                <p class=\"lead\">Midotwn on Campus is committed to giving every student at the University of Texas the opportunity to experience the life-changing reality of Jesus Christ. Follow us on Twitter @HCBConCAMPUS for the most up to date information on events and meeting locations.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"bg-light-gray\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\r\n                <h2 c