are fully retained and undiminished by the union. We believe Jesus died on the cross as a substitute for sinful humanity, was buried, rose bodily from the tomb, ascended into Heaven where He ministers on the behalf of those who have trusted in Him, and someday will come again for His own. (John 1:18, 8:58, Matt. 1:23, Col. 1:15-17, 1 Tim. 1:15, 3:16). \r\n                </p>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </section>\r\n        </section>','What We Believe','','inherit','closed','open','','1057-revision-v1','','','2015-08-04 17:50:16','2015-08-04 17:50:16','',1057,'http://www.midtownaustin.org/2015/08/04/1057-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1075,4,'2015-08-04 17:52:12','2015-08-04 17:52:12','<!-- PAGE HEADING \r\n================================================== -->\r\n<section class=\"parallax parallax-giving\" style=\"background-image: url(https://scontent-dfw1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xaf1/t31.0-8/s2048x2048/10256695_519143751529359_361980284696071893_o.jpg);\">\r\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"container\">\r\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n                    <h1>What We Believe</h1>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n<!-- /.page heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- PAGE CONTENT \r\n================================================== -->\r\n<!-- Standard Section - White Background -->\r\n<section id=\"article\" class=\"wrapper wrapper-primary\">\r\n          <div class=\"container text-center\"> \r\n            <div class=\"row\">\r\n              <div class=\"col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 \">\r\n                  <h2>Our Mission</h2>\r\n                  <hr>\r\n                  <p class=\"lead\">    \r\nThe Mission for the Church was given by Christ and is unchanging, that we would  \"Go therefore and make disciples of all nations, baptizing them in the name of the Father and of the Son and 