. Fall Retreat is the best way to grow in your relationship with others in our community. We spend time eating, playing, worshipping, talking, and learning together. It\'s one of the best weekends of the year and you won\'t want to miss it!</p><a href=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/2015/08/04/student-fall-retreat-2015/\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Read More</a></div><div class=\"col-sm-4\"><h4><a href=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/2015/08/03/winter-conference-2016/\">Winter Conference 2016</a></h4><p><img src=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/ut-college-winter-conference-2016.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive img-thumbnail\"></p><p><strong>Date</strong>: January 1-5, 2015<br>\r\n<strong>Location</strong>: Fort Worth, Texas<br>\r\n<strong>Cost</strong>:<br>\r\n$200 if you register and pay deposit by Oct 15<br>\r\n$230 if you register and pay deposit by Dec 5<br>\r\n$260 after December 5<br>\r\n<strong>Event Website</strong>:  Winter Conference Details<br>\r\n<strong>Sign up here</strong>: Conference Registration<br>\r\nThis year we are partnering with CRU for Winter Conference and Summer Projects. At Winter Conference, you will get to worship with college students from all over the region, hear from incredible speakers like Tom Nelson and enjoy the city of Ft. Worth with your friends.</p><a href=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/2015/08/03/winter-conference-2016/\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Read More</a></div><div class=\"col-sm-4\"><h4><a href=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/2015/08/02/beach-retreat-2016/\">Beach Retreat 2016</a></h4><p><img src=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/longhorn-college-summer-project-2016-disney-world.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive img-thumbnail\"></p><p><strong>Date</strong>: March 13-20th, 2016<br>\r\n<strong>Location</strong>: South Padre Island, Texas<br>\r\n<strong>Cost</strong>:<br> \r\n$360 student in a hotel<br>\r\n$250 student camping on the beach (men only)<br>\r\n<strong>Event Website</strong>: Beach Reach<b