nter\">\r\n                <div class=\"icon-box boxed\">\r\n                    <h3>New To Jesus?</h3>\r\n                    <p>Midtown is a church that invites people to explore, ask questions and grow in their faith. Click below to learn more about what we believe and how the gospel is good news for everyone. </p>\r\n                    <a href=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/im-new-to-jesus/\" class=\"btn btn-success\">Dive Deeper</a>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-md-4 text-center\">\r\n                <div class=\"icon-box boxed\">\r\n                    <h3>New To Austin?</h3>\r\n                    <p>Welcome to the <a href=\"http://austin.blog.statesman.com/2015/08/03/atx-best-large-city/\" title=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\">greatest city in America</a>! We love Austin and we want you to love Austin too. Click below to see our recommendations of places to eat, things to do and more.  </p>\r\n                    <a href=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/im-new-to-austin/\" class=\"btn btn-success\">Have Some Fun</a>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<!-- Podcasts Section -->\r\n<section class=\"bg-light-gray\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"h-lines hl-2\">Sermon Podcasts</h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            [rpbj category=\"3\" posts=\"4\" excerpt=\"true\" meta=\"true\" buttonclass=\"btn-primary\" buttontext=\"Listen\" container=\"col-sm-3\"]\r\n			<div id=\"home-podcast-button\" class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\r\n                <p><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-warning btn-lg\"><i class=\"fa fa-archive\"></i> View Podcast Archives</button></p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>','Home','','inherit','closed','open','','4-revision-v1','','','2015-08-06 17:57:03','2015-08-06 17:57:03','',4,'http://www.midtownaustin.org/2015/08/06/4-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1253,1,'2015-08-06 18:00:35','2015-08-06 18:00:35','<section class=\"parallax parallax-giving\" style=\"background-image: url(https://scontent-dfw1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xaf1/t31.0-8/s2048x2048/10256695_519143751529359_361980284696071893_o.jpg);\">\r\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"container\">\r\n                <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\r\n                    <h1 title=\"Purpose and Vision of Midtown Church - Central Austin and Campus Ministry\">Purpose &amp; Vision</h1>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section>\r\n	<div class=\"container\">\r\n		<div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-12 text-center\">\r\n				<h2 class=\"h-lines hl-2\">Midtown Church</h2>\r\n				<p class=\"lead\">A family loved and served by God, compelled to love and serve Austin with God.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"bg-dark-teal\">\r\n	<div class=\"container\">\r\n		<div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-12 text-center\">\r\n				<h2 class=\"h-lines hl-3\">Vision</h2>\r\n				<p class=\"lead\">Our central purpose is to glorify God in all things. Our vision is to partner with God to see the day when every man, woman and child hears the gospel from a person who loves them &mdash; beginning in Austin.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"bg-light-gray\">\r\n	<div class=\"container\">\r\n		<div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n				<img src=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/love-church-central-austin.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive img-thumbnail\">\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-9\">\r\n				<h3>Love</h3>\r\n				<p><strong><em>(Matthew 22:36-40)</em></strong><br>\r\nWe love God because God loved us first. He loved us when we didn’t love Him. He loves us when we fail to love Him. We love Him because he knows everything about us and still loves us. God loves us, therefore we love God.</p>\r\n				<p>We love people because people matter to God. God loves everyone; every man, woman & child. Which means God loves imperfect people like us and so we love imperfect people too. God loves people, therefore we love people.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-3 col-sm-push-9\">\r\n				<img src=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/serving-one-another-in-austin.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive img-thumbnail\">\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-9 col-sm-pull-3\">\r\n				<h3>Serve</h3>\r\n				<p><strong><em>(Mark 10:45)</em></strong><br>\r\nJesus came to serve. He gave his life serving. As his followers we chose to use our lives to serve. We chose to serve people who are not like us and who do not like us. We serve people who ask and people who don’t have a voice to ask. We serve the least, the hurting the lonely and the marginalized. We serve because people matter to God. We serve to give people a picture of our God who serves. Jesus came to serve, therefore we are here to serve.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n				<img src=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/central-austin-church.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive img-thumbnail\">\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-9\">\r\n				<h3>Austin</h3>\r\n				<p><strong><em>(Jeremiah 29:7)</em></strong><br>\r\n				God has given us a passion for our city; this is where we are called to love & serve.</p>\r\n				<p>We love Austin. We love its culture, its people and its places. As Central Austinites we want to do our part in helping Austin become an even more weird, fun, creative, green and loving city. We hope for a day that every person in Austin has an opportunity to hear about God’s love for them from a friend who loves them.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</section>','Purpose & Vision','','inherit','closed','open','','956-revision-v1','','','2015-08-06 18:00:35','2015-08-06 18:00:35','',956,'http://www.midtownaustin.org/2015/08/06/956-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1254,1,'2015-08-06 18:00:58','2015-08-06 18:00:58','<section class=\"parallax parallax-giving\" style=\"background-image: url(https://scontent-dfw1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xaf1/t31.0-8/s2048x2048/10256695_519143751529359_361980284696071893_o.jpg);\">\r\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"container\">\r\n                <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\r\n                    <h1 title=\"Purpose and Vision of Midtown Church - Central Austin and Campus Ministry\">Purpose &amp; Vision</h1>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section>\r\n	<div class=\"container\">\r\n		<div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-12 text-center\">\r\n				<h2 class=\"h-lines hl-2\">Midtown Church</h2>\r\n				<p class=\"lead\">A family loved and served by God, compelled to love and serve Austin with God.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"bg-dark-teal\">\r\n	<div class=\"container\">\r\n		<div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-12 text-center\">\r\n				<h2 class=\"h-lines hl-3\">Vision</h2>\r\n				<p class=\"lead\">Our central purpose is to glorify God in all things. Our vision is to partner with God to see the day when every man, woman and child hears the gospel from a person who loves them &mdash; beginning in Austin and spreading to the ends of the earth.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"bg-light-gray\">\r\n	<div class=\"container\">\r\n		<div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n				<img src=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/love-church-central-austin.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive img-thumbnail\">\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-9\">\r\n				<h3>Love</h3>\r\n				<p><strong><em>(Matthew 22:36-40)</em></strong><br>\r\nWe love God because God loved us first. He loved us when we didn’t love Him. He loves us when we fail to love Him. We love Him because he knows everything about us and still loves us. God loves us, therefore we love God.</p>\r\n				<p>We love people because people matter to God. God loves everyone; every man, woman & child. Which means God loves imperfect people like us and so we love imperfect people too. God loves people, therefore we love people.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-3 col-sm-push-9\">\r\n				<img src=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/serving-one-another-in-austin.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive img-thumbnail\">\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-9 col-sm-pull-3\">\r\n				<h3>Serve</h3>\r\n				<p><strong><em>(Mark 10:45)</em></strong><br>\r\nJesus came to serve. He gave his life serving. As his followers we chose to use our lives to serve. We chose to serve people who are not like us and who do not like us. We serve people who ask and people who don’t have a voice to ask. We serve the least, the hurting the lonely and the marginalized. We serve because people matter to God. We serve to give people a picture of our God who serves. Jesus came to serve, therefore we are here to serve.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n				<img src=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/central-austin-church.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive img-thumbnail\">\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-9\">\r\n				<h3>Austin</h3>\r\n				<p><strong><em>(Jeremiah 29:7)</em></strong><br>\r\n				God has given us a passion for our city; this is where we are called to love & serve.</p>\r\n				<p>We love Austin. We love its culture, its people and its places. As Central Austinites we want to do our part in helping Austin become an even more weird, fun, creative, green and loving city. We hope for a day that every person in Austin has an opportunity to hear about God’s love for them from a friend who loves them.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</section>','Purpose & Vision','','inherit','closed','open','','956-revision-v1','','','2015-08-06 18:00:58','2015-08-06 18:00:58','',956,'http://www.midtownaustin.org/2015/08/06/956-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1255,1,'2015-08-06 18:02:57','2015-08-06 18:02:57','<section class=\"parallax parallax-sunday\" style=\"background-image: url(http://i.istockimg.com/image-zoom/17906621/3/380/253/zoom-17906621-3.jpg);\">\r\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"container\">\r\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n                    <h1>Midtown Church College Ministry</h1>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section>\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\r\n				<h2 class=\"h-lines hl-2\">Midtown on Campus</h2>\r\n                <p class=\"lead\">Hill Country on Campus is committed to giving every student at the University of Texas the opportunity to experience the life-changing reality of Jesus Christ. Follow us on Twitter @HCBConCAMPUS for the most up to date information on events and meeting locations.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"bg-light-gray\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"h-gray h-lines hl-1\">Community Life</h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-7\">\r\n				<h3>College Small Groups</h3>\r\n                <p>At Midtown Church, we long to grow in our relationship with God in the context of community. We believe this best happens as we are Godward, Inward, and Outward.</p>\r\n				<ul class=\"list-group\">\r\n					<li class=\"list-group-item\">\r\n						<strong>Godward</strong> &mdash; We strive to glorify God and enjoy Him in everything we do.\r\n					</li>\r\n					<li class=\"list-group-item\">\r\n						<strong>Inward</strong> &mdash; We believe it is vital that we invest deeply in each other and encourage each other to fully trust in Jesus.\r\n					</li>\r\n					<li class=\"list-group-item\">\r\n						<strong>Outward</strong> &mdash; We are committed to actively, intentionally, and consistently engaging people with the life-changing reality of Jesus Christ.\r\n					</li>\r\n				</ul>\r\n				<p>For Hill Country on Campus, the majority of our small groups are on Wednesday nights in the Texas Union. We meet at 8pm for 30 - 45 minutes as one large group for worship, games, and a short talk before breaking up into small groups. This semester we are reading through Acts, Nehemiah, and Proverbs. If you are interested in joining a small group, come any Wednesday or email Brad at brad@midtownaustin.org.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-5\">\r\n				<h3>Discipleship</h3>\r\n				<p>We believe that Jesus clearly gave the mandate in Matthew 28:18-20 to \"make disciples of all nations.\" At Mditown, one place we are committed to pursuing this commission is on the University of Texas Campus. We seek to provide all of our students the opportunity to both be discipled and engage in disciple-making which includes a specific focus in evangelism training. We believe that a multiplying movement of disciples is the most effective way to reach the ends of the earth with gospel, and we seek to labor with the strength of Christ to that end.</p>\r\n				<p>If you would like to learn more about our ministry philosophy on the campus of Texas, or if you would like to get involved in discipleship relationships and evangelism training then please contact Brad Laws at brad@midtownaustin.org</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section>\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\r\n				<h2 class=\"h-gray h-lines hl-1\">Upcoming Events</h2>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n				[rpbj category=\"4\" posts=\"6\" excerpt=\"true\" image=\"true\" buttonclass=\"btn-primary\" buttontext=\"Read More\" container=\"col-sm-4\"]\r\n			</div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n','College','','inherit','closed','open','','981-revision-v1','','','2015-08-06 18:02:57','2015-08-06 18:02:57','',981,'http://www.midtownaustin.org/2015/08/06/981-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1256,1,'2015-08-06 18:03:11','2015-08-06 18:03:11','<section class=\"parallax parallax-sunday\" style=\"background-image: url(http://i.istockimg.com/image-zoom/17906621/3/380/253/zoom-17906621-3.jpg);\">\r\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"container\">\r\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n                    <h1>Midtown Church College Ministry</h1>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section>\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\r\n				<h2 class=\"h-lines hl-2\">Hill Country on Campus</h2>\r\n                <p class=\"lead\">Hill Country on Campus is committed to giving every student at the University of Texas the opportunity to experience the life-changing reality of Jesus Christ. Follow us on Twitter @HCBConCAMPUS for the most up to date information on events and meeting locations.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"bg-light-gray\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"h-gray h-lines hl-1\">Community Life</h