:15','2015-08-06 18:22:15','',1181,'http://www.midtownaustin.org/2015/08/06/1181-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1262,1,'2015-08-06 18:26:25','2015-08-06 18:26:25','','midtown-church-austin-merging-with-hill-country-central','','inherit','closed','open','','midtown-church-austin-merging-with-hill-country-central','','','2015-08-21 20:01:37','2015-08-21 20:01:37','',0,'http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/midtown-church-austin-merging-with-hill-country-central.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1263,1,'2015-08-06 19:43:32','2015-08-06 19:43:32','<!-- PAGE HEADING \n================================================== -->\n<section class=\"parallax parallax-giving\" style=\"background-image: url(https://scontent-dfw1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xaf1/t31.0-8/s2048x2048/10256695_519143751529359_361980284696071893_o.jpg);\">\n	<div class=\"container-fluid\">\n		<div class=\"row\">\n			<div class=\"container\">\n				<div class=\"text-center\">\n					<h1>What We Believe</h1>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</section>\n<!-- /.page heading -->\n\n<!-- PAGE CONTENT \n================================================== -->\n<!-- Standard Section - White Background -->\n<section id=\"article\" class=\"wrapper wrapper-primary\">\n	<div class=\"container text-center\"> \n		<div class=\"row\">\n			<div class=\"col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 \">\n				<p class=\"lead\">\n					Midtown Church affirms orthodox Christian doctrines. This means we adhere to some of the most ancient creeds of the faith including the Nicene Creed. The following seven statements succinctly state our core beliefs, which we uphold unity on and allow for diverse opinions about others. We do not endorse dogmatic teaching about secondary matters.\n				</p>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"bg-light-gray\">\n	<div class=\"container\">\n		<div class=\"row\">\n			<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n				<h4>The Authority and Inerrancy of Scripture</h4>\n				<p>We believe the Bible, as revealed to us in the Old and New Testaments, is the inspired Word of God and is our final authority and without error in its original manuscripts.</p>\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n				<h4>The Trinity: Father, Son, and Holy Spirit</h4>\n				<p>We believe in One God who exists eternally as three co-equal, fully divine persons, the Father, Son, and Holy Spirit.</p>\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n				<h4>The Full Deity and Humanity of Jesus</h4>\n				<p>We believe that God Incarnate, Jesus Christ, is both fully God and fully human at the same time.</p>\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n				<h4>The Dignity and Depravity of the Human Race</h4>\n				<p>We believe that every person has inherent worth and value because they are created in the image of God, and yet that every person is a sinner by nature and by choice and unable to justify themselves before God based on their own deeds.</p>\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n				<h4>The Substitutionary Atonement and Bodily Resurrection of Jesus Christ</h4>\n				<p>We believe that Jesus died in our place for our sins, was buried, and then was physically resurrected to new life.ithout error in its original manuscripts.</p>\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n				<h4>Salvation by Grace Alone through Faith Alone in Christ Alone</h4>\n				<p>We believe that people are reconciled to God and reborn to eternal life by the grace of God through faith in Jesus Christ and not as the result of any human efforts.</p>\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n				<h4>The Future Physical Return of Jesus Christ</h4>\n				<p>We believe that Jesus Christ will return to the earth in the future to finalize His work of redemption and restoration.</p>\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n				Feel free to continue reading a full affirmation of faith <a href=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/full-statement-of-faith/\" title=\"undefined\" target=\"\">here</a>.\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</section>','What We 