ake disciples of all nations.\" At Mditown, one place we are committed to pursuing this commission is on the University of Texas Campus. We seek to provide all of our students the opportunity to both be discipled and engage in disciple-making which includes a specific focus in evangelism training. We believe that a multiplying movement of disciples is the most effective way to reach the ends of the earth with gospel, and we seek to labor with the strength of Christ to that end.</p>\r\n				<p>If you would like to learn more about our ministry philosophy on the campus of Texas, or if you would like to get involved in discipleship relationships and evangelism training then please contact Brad Laws at brad@midtownaustin.org</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section>\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\r\n				<h2 class=\"h-gray h-lines hl-1\">Upcoming Events</h2>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n				[rpbj category=\"4\" posts=\"6\" excerpt=\"true\" image=\"true\" buttonclass=\"btn-primary\" buttontext=\"Read More\" container=\"col-sm-4\"]\r\n			</div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n','College','','inherit','closed','open','','981-revision-v1','','','2015-08-07 18:18:56','2015-08-07 18:18:56','',981,'http://www.midtownaustin.org/2015/08/07/981-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1284,1,'2015-08-07 18:25:00','2015-08-07 18:25:00','','midtown-church-sunday-morning-service-central-austin','','inherit','closed','open','','midtown-church-sunday-morning-service-central-austin','','','2015-08-07 18:25:00','2015-08-07 18:25:00','',923,'http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/midtown-church-sunday-morning-service-central-austin.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1285,1,'2015-08-07 18:25:24','2015-08-07 18:25:24','<script src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps/api/js?sensor=false\"></script>\r\n    <script>	\r\n \r\n      function init