n            <div class=\"col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 text-center\">\r\n				<h2 class=\"h-gray h-lines hl-1\">The Gospel of John: That You May Believe</h2>\r\n                <p>John, one of Jesus’ closest disciples, sums up his eye witness account of Jesus’ life with these words, “these are written so that you may believe that Jesus is the Christ, the Son of God, and that by believing you may have life in his name” (John 20:31). Join us this summer as we pick back up in our study of the Gospel of John to explore why we too can believe that life is truly found in his name.</p>\r\n				<img src=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/current-series-the-gospel-of-john.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive\">\r\n                <p class=\"lead\">Join us on <a href=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/sunday-mornings/\" title=\"undefined\" target=\"\">Sunday Mornings</a> at 10:45am and/or connect with us throughout the week in a <a href=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/midtown-communities/\" title=\"undefined\" target=\"\">Midtown Community</a>.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>','Current Series','','inherit','closed','open','','1081-revision-v1','','','2015-08-07 18:49:24','2015-08-07 18:49:24','',1081,'http://www.midtownaustin.org/2015/08/07/1081-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1304,1,'2015-08-07 19:00:24','2015-08-07 19:00:24','<!-- Page Heading -->\r\n<!-- Parallax Section -->\r\n<section class=\"parallax\" style=\"background-image: url(http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/midtown-church-page-header-background.jpg);\">\r\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"container\">\r\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n                    <h1>Giving &mdash; An Act of Worship</h1>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n<!-- /.page heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- Page Content -->\r\n\r\n<section>\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 text-center\">\r\n                <p class=\"lead\">Jesus is the most generous person who ever lived. He gave his life so that we might live. As Christians, we give our time, talent, and money joyfully in response to Jesus’ generosity and to help more people meet Jesus.</p>\r\n\r\n                <p>As a community, we take joy in the ways our faith is made stronger through giving and receiving together. There is a satisfaction that comes from following Jesus’ example of generosity toward those most in need, and it is a privilege to use our resources and time to continue telling God’s story and help bring measurable change in the world.</p>\r\n\r\n                <p>Below are some ways for you to give to the ministry of Midtown Church.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"bg-light-gray\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"h-lines hl-2\">Ways to Give</h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-6 text-center\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"h-gray\">Online</h2>\r\n                <p>You can give via credit card or bank withdrawal either one time or recurring. Click the button below to begin.</p>\r\n                <p><a href=\"https://midtownchurch.cloverdonations.com/give/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"btn btn-warning btn-lg\">Click Here to Give Online</a></p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-6 text-center\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"h-gray\">Cash &amp; Checks</h2>\r\n                <p>Please make checks payable to Midtown Church and drop them in the offering plate on Sunday or mail to:</p>\r\n                <address>\r\n                    Midtown Church<br>\r\n                    4809 Sinclair Ave<br>\r\n                    Austin, TX 78756\r\n                </address>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section>\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"h-gray h-lines hl-1\">Volunteering</h2>\r\n                <p>If you’ve been served by Midtown Church, whether it be through greeters on Sundays, teachers in you child’s classroom, enjoying a cup of coffee before service, musicians on stage leading us in worship, or any number of other ways—chances are you’ve been served by a faithful volunteer giving up time and talent to serve Jesus by serving you. At Midtown, we intentionally keep our budget and staff small and rely on a community of volunteers who love Jesus and love to serve his church.</p>\r\n                <p>If you consider Midtown your church, we ask you to serve as a volunteer. By doing so, you’re an essential part of helping others meet Jesus. And if you’re a member, you’ve committed to serve generously as part of your membership covenant.</p>\r\n                <p>There are a number of opportunities to serve at Midtown. To find out how you can serve, contact Adam Brunson at adam@midtownaustin.org</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>','Give','','inherit','closed','open','','935-revision-v1','','','2015-08-07 19:00:24','2015-08-07 19:00:24','',935,'http://www.midtownaustin.org/2015/08/07/935-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1305,1,'2015-08-07 19:03:20','2015-08-07 19:03:20','','lunches-with-midtown-church','','inherit','closed','open','','lunches-with-midtown-church','','','2015-08-21 18:47:53','2015-08-21 18:47:53','',1181,'http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/lunches-with-midtown-church.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1306,1,'2015-08-08 01:42:09','2015-08-08 01:42:09','<div class=\"form-group\">\r\n<label>Name</label>\r\n[text* Name class:form-control placeholder \"Your Name\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"form-