ontainer\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"h-lines hl-2\">Where &amp; When</h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-5\">\r\n                <h4>The Baker School</h4>\r\n                <address>\r\n                    3908 Avenue B<br>\r\n                    Austin, TX 78751\r\n                </address>\r\n                <p>Doors open at 10:15am for snacks, delicious Anderson\'s Coffee, and/or\r\n                time to get your kiddos checked in for their class. Worship begins at\r\n                10:45am.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div id=\"map-container\" class=\"col-sm-7\"></div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section>\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-6 text-center\">\r\n                <h3>What to Expect</h3>\r\n                <p>When you get there, grab some coffee and meet someone or just head right into the auditorium. Knowing that Jesus has truly paid it all for us helps our worship environment have a relaxed and casual feel. We will sing some songs, hear a sermon about Jesus from the Bible, take communion, and say a few prayers. That’s about it! We welcome all people to join with us in our Sunday celebration of Jesus.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-6 text-center\">\r\n                <h3>What About Kids?</h3>\r\n                <p>While you are in the worship service we have fun and engaging classes for kids (nursery through elementary school) that will help them worship God according to their age level. We will always let you know what is being taught and classes are always optional.</p>\r\n                <p>We invite all middle school and high school students to worship with the adults.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>','Sunday Mornings','','inherit','closed','open','','923-revision-v1','','','2015-08-21 15:53:34','2015-08-21 15:53:34','',923,'http://www.midtownaustin.org/2015/08/21/923-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1335,1,'2015-08-21 15:53:57','2015-08-21 15:53:57','<!-- Carousel\r\n================================================== -->\r\n<div id=\"myCarousel\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\">\r\n    <!-- Indicators -->\r\n    <ol class=\"carousel-indicators\">\r\n        <li data-target=\"#myCarousel\" data-slide-to=\"0\" class=\"active\"></li>\r\n        <li data-target=\"#myCarousel\" data-slide-to=\"1\"></li>\r\n    </ol>\r\n    <div class=\"carousel-inner\" role=\"listbox\">\r\n		<!-- Slide 1 - Inline style needed in order to use WP Media -->\r\n        <div class=\"item first-slide\" style=\"background:\r\n        linear-gradient(\r\n            rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25),\r\n            rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25)\r\n        ),\r\n        url(http://www.midtownaustin.org/wp-content/uploads/central-austin-church-sunday-morning.jpg); background-size: cover;\">\r\n            <div class=\"carousel-caption div-desktop\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"shadow-text\">Join us on Sundays at The Baker School. Doors open at 10:15 and Service Starts at 10:45.</h2>\r\n                <p>\r\n                    <a class=\"btn btn-lg btn-warning\" href=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/sunday-mornings/\" role=\"button\">Click here for a map and other Sunday morning info...</a>\r\n                </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n			<div class=\"carousel-caption div-mobile\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"shadow-text\">Join us on Sundays at 10:45am</h2>\r\n                <p>\r\n                    <a class=\"btn btn-lg btn-warning\" href=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/sunday-mornings/\" role=\"button\">Click here for more info...</a>\r\n                </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n		<!-- Slide 2 -->\r\n        <div class=\"item active second-slide\" style=\"background:\r\n		linear-gradient(\r\n            rgba(25