ers fa-5x\"></i>\r\n                    <h5>Sunday Mornings</h5></a>\r\n                    <p>Doors open at 10:15am for coffee and conversation, then worship starts at 10:45am on Sunday mornings at the Baker School in Hyde Park</p>\r\n                    <a href=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/sunday-mornings/\" class=\"btn btn-success\">Get More Info</a>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n                <div class=\"equal-height\">\r\n                    <a href=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/college/\" title=\"undefined\" target=\"\"><i class=\"fa fa-university fa-5x\"></i>\r\n                    <h5>On Campus</h5></a>\r\n                    <p>Hill Country on Campus is Midtown\'s College Ministry. It takes place on Wednesday nights in the Texas Union at 8:00pm.</p>\r\n                    <a href=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/college/\" class=\"btn btn-success\">Learn More</a>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n                <div class=\"equal-height\">\r\n                    <a href=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/midtown-communities/\" title=\"undefined\" target=\"\"><i class=\"fa fa-users fa-5x\"></i>\r\n                    <h5>Midtown Communities</h5></a>\r\n                    <p>Our Midtown Communities gather throughout the week to care for each other and fulfill Jesus\' mission of being disciples who make disciples.</p>\r\n                    <a href=\"http://www.midtownaustin.org/midtown-communities/\" class=\"btn btn-success\">Find a Group</a>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section id=\"news\" class=\"bg-dark-teal\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"h-lines hl-3\">News &amp; Events</h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n			[rpbj category=\"5\" posts=\"4\" image=\"true\